WEBVTT

02:10.680 --> 02:11.610
Is it delicious?

02:12.710 --> 02:14.590
How about you eat first?

02:15.400 --> 02:16.520
No.

02:16.520 --> 02:18.030
Mo, you should eat first.

02:18.280 --> 02:20.310
I want to sit on my favorite swing,

02:20.310 --> 02:22.430
eating my favorite candied hawthorns.

02:22.430 --> 02:22.870
Okay.

02:23.310 --> 02:23.840
Let's go.

03:12.750 --> 03:13.400
Uncle Lie.

03:13.400 --> 03:14.240
Father.

03:16.000 --> 03:18.280
Uncle Lie, what happened to your leg?

03:18.520 --> 03:19.560
Go, quickly.

03:20.190 --> 03:20.680
Hurry.

03:21.079 --> 03:22.540
Let's climb over the wall.

03:33.030 --> 03:33.680
Han Mo.

03:33.680 --> 03:36.000
Yunling, I'm scared.

03:36.750 --> 03:37.800
Han Mo.

03:40.840 --> 03:42.240
Han Mo! Han Mo!

04:10.630 --> 04:12.070
General Xiao, you're carrying the badge
bestowed by His Majesty

04:12.070 --> 04:13.520
to enter the Imperial Prison.

04:13.520 --> 04:14.450
I can't stop you.

04:14.680 --> 04:15.240
But,

04:15.240 --> 04:16.920
as for Han Mo's case,

04:17.120 --> 04:19.000
I think you'd better not look into it.

04:19.000 --> 04:19.800
Why?

04:20.120 --> 04:22.240
Is it possible that Han Mo's case file

04:22.240 --> 04:23.870
has something fishy about it?

04:23.870 --> 04:24.720
Absolutely not.

04:24.720 --> 04:26.250
It's just that this case...

04:36.190 --> 04:37.630
Take me to see Han Mo right now.

04:37.630 --> 04:39.270
He is a heavily punished criminal here.

04:39.270 --> 04:40.600
Without His Majesty's decree,

04:40.600 --> 04:41.600
you cannot see him.

04:41.600 --> 04:42.430
What?

04:43.070 --> 04:45.530
This doesn't count
as His Majesty's decree?

04:45.680 --> 04:46.870
It counts.

04:47.390 --> 04:48.920
General Xiao, please come this way.

04:48.920 --> 04:50.120
I'll take you there.

04:54.270 --> 04:55.600
General Xiao, this way.

05:05.720 --> 05:06.630
General Xiao.

05:06.630 --> 05:08.120
He is the most special prisoner here.

05:08.120 --> 05:09.360
I was ordered to keep him strung up

05:09.360 --> 05:10.310
upside down during the day

05:10.310 --> 05:11.770
and take him down at night.

05:11.830 --> 05:13.600
When I became
the Ministry of Justice's historian,

05:13.600 --> 05:15.070
the previous historian
instructed me to do so.

05:15.070 --> 05:17.240
It has been done for many years.

05:18.870 --> 05:19.870
Are you Han Mo?

05:22.560 --> 05:23.390
Han Mo.

05:25.560 --> 05:26.360
Han Mo.

05:39.950 --> 05:40.750
Han Yunling.

05:41.510 --> 05:42.310
Han Yunling.

05:44.120 --> 05:44.920
Han Yunling.

05:50.480 --> 05:52.920
What are you doing
in the middle of the night?

05:52.920 --> 05:54.070
Come with me right now.

05:54.070 --> 05:55.070
Han Mo is dying.

06:22.510 --> 06:24.680
I'll go outside
and guard the main door for you.

06:24.680 --> 06:25.390
Okay.

06:58.270 --> 07:00.240
Thank you for helping me find my cousin.

07:00.240 --> 07:01.360
As long as it's him.

07:01.360 --> 07:03.240
Take a look quickly.

07:06.920 --> 07:07.680
Mo.

07:08.800 --> 07:09.600
Mo.

07:17.190 --> 07:18.000
Here.

07:32.310 --> 07:33.120
Mo.

07:36.120 --> 07:36.600
You are?

07:36.950 --> 07:38.270
I am your cousin.

07:38.870 --> 07:40.120
I'm here to save you.

07:41.830 --> 07:42.870
Yunling.

07:47.510 --> 07:49.390
Save me.

07:52.310 --> 07:53.120
Mo.

07:54.270 --> 07:55.470
What happened to him?

08:06.510 --> 08:08.870
He is already dead.

08:16.920 --> 08:18.600
Oh, Chief Shen.

08:18.600 --> 08:19.600
Why didn't you

08:19.600 --> 08:21.630
have someone inform us
in advance before you came?

08:21.630 --> 08:22.190
What?

08:22.190 --> 08:24.720
Do I have to report to you
when I visit the Imperial Prison?

08:24.720 --> 08:25.310
That's not what I meant.

08:25.310 --> 08:26.390
You are the Chief.

08:26.390 --> 08:28.270
Who can stop you, right?

08:28.270 --> 08:29.630
Cut the crap.

08:29.720 --> 08:31.830
Lord Zhang is in a bad mood today.

08:34.789 --> 08:35.909
Chief.

08:37.720 --> 08:38.750
Hurry up and leave.

08:38.750 --> 08:39.809
Someone is coming.

08:40.120 --> 08:41.120
Don't get caught.

08:42.030 --> 08:42.840
No.

09:01.440 --> 09:03.270
Why are you dawdling?

09:03.270 --> 09:04.000
You guard the prison,

09:04.000 --> 09:05.530
and you can't find the keys?

09:09.870 --> 09:11.720
You old fart,

09:11.720 --> 09:12.670
why don't you carry

09:12.670 --> 09:13.510
such important things with you?

09:13.510 --> 09:14.080
You're right.

09:14.080 --> 09:15.120
I'm telling you,

09:15.120 --> 09:16.630
if he gets away,

09:16.790 --> 09:18.270
Lord Zhang will kill your whole family.

09:18.270 --> 09:18.750
I know.

09:19.790 --> 09:20.870
Lord Zhang.

09:21.720 --> 09:22.870
Which Lord Zhang?

09:25.720 --> 09:27.600
Go away.

09:33.240 --> 09:36.320
As usual, lock the door and get lost.

09:36.320 --> 09:37.790
Come back

09:38.120 --> 09:39.120
when we're done.

09:39.120 --> 09:39.750
Yes.

09:44.000 --> 09:45.270
So quiet.

09:45.790 --> 09:47.030
Playing dead?

09:47.390 --> 09:49.440
It's useless to play dead today.

09:49.440 --> 09:50.600
You can't escape

09:50.600 --> 09:51.910
this torture.

09:52.600 --> 09:53.360
Beat him!

09:53.360 --> 09:54.120
Yes.

09:58.080 --> 09:59.320
Playing dead, huh?

09:59.320 --> 10:00.000
Fine.

10:00.360 --> 10:02.080
Watch me beat you to death.

10:03.030 --> 10:03.870
Pretend.

10:04.390 --> 10:05.390
Keep pretending.

10:05.390 --> 10:06.390
Playing dead?

10:08.080 --> 10:10.120
They won't even spare Mo's corpse.

10:10.120 --> 10:11.480
I'll fight them!

10:12.440 --> 10:13.240
Playing dead?

10:14.120 --> 10:15.270
Calm down now.

10:16.670 --> 10:17.670
Calm down.

10:18.870 --> 10:20.200
Beat him to death!

10:20.600 --> 10:21.150
Beat him!

10:23.120 --> 10:25.360
They even humiliate Mo's corpse.

10:25.360 --> 10:26.200
What kind of deep hatred

10:26.200 --> 10:27.870
do the Hans have against them

10:27.870 --> 10:28.600
that they won't even

10:28.600 --> 10:30.200
spare a dead man's corpse?

10:31.910 --> 10:32.440
Actually,

10:32.440 --> 10:34.670
I've always felt that Han Mo's case

10:34.670 --> 10:35.550
is fishy.

10:35.720 --> 10:37.480
He was locked up
in the Imperial Prison alone

10:37.480 --> 10:38.910
for more than a decade.

10:39.200 --> 10:40.390
Tortured every day,

10:40.480 --> 10:41.510
yet kept alive.

10:42.390 --> 10:43.670
If it wasn't a deep hatred,

10:43.670 --> 10:44.910
there was no need for this.

10:44.910 --> 10:45.510
Moreover,

10:46.030 --> 10:47.360
I checked his case file.

10:47.840 --> 10:49.200
It's completely blank.

10:49.630 --> 10:50.490
Think about it.

10:50.840 --> 10:53.790
Who exactly persecuted
the Han family back then?

10:55.390 --> 10:56.520
Leave no survivors!

11:02.270 --> 11:04.130
Forget what should be forgotten.

11:04.510 --> 11:05.910
Live well.

11:10.510 --> 11:12.150
I injured my head at the time

11:12.150 --> 11:13.720
and don't remember many things.

11:13.720 --> 11:15.600
Uncle Lie rarely mentioned it either.

11:15.600 --> 11:17.390
Later, whenever I asked him about it,

11:17.390 --> 11:19.200
he always said it was in the past,

11:19.440 --> 11:21.300
and told us to live in the present.

11:22.720 --> 11:23.450
Don't worry,

11:24.080 --> 11:25.080
I'm here.

11:25.840 --> 11:27.840
I will find out the truth for you.

11:32.080 --> 11:34.410
But I have one more presumptuous request.

11:34.910 --> 11:35.720
Tell me.

11:37.910 --> 11:40.240
Can you give me Mo's body?

11:40.270 --> 11:43.530
I want to take him back to Changmo
to reunite with Uncle Lie.

11:43.790 --> 11:45.030
About the body...

11:51.080 --> 11:51.960
About the body,

11:52.200 --> 11:53.800
I will figure something out.

11:59.670 --> 12:02.070
You haven't been treated for several days.

12:02.670 --> 12:04.600
Let me give you acupuncture first.

12:04.720 --> 12:06.390
Let's skip it today.

12:06.480 --> 12:07.550
Get some good rest.

12:08.270 --> 12:10.270
I'll go figure something out first.

12:16.750 --> 12:18.320
Lord Li,

12:18.720 --> 12:21.630
give me a reply.

12:22.150 --> 12:23.720
Oh, Lord Wang,

12:23.720 --> 12:25.480
calm down.

12:25.720 --> 12:28.510
His Majesty told you to stay home
without any duties.

12:28.510 --> 12:29.910
He didn't say anything against you.

12:29.910 --> 12:31.320
He hasn't charged you with anything.

12:31.320 --> 12:32.910
Why are you panicking?

12:33.480 --> 12:34.750
Besides,

12:34.750 --> 12:35.810
about this matter,

12:36.240 --> 12:39.320
why don't you go to Lord Zhang?

12:39.510 --> 12:41.080
Ah, Lord Zhang.

12:41.080 --> 12:43.440
He is extremely rigid.

12:43.600 --> 12:44.360
Moreover,

12:44.360 --> 12:45.870
would he

12:46.080 --> 12:47.320
go to His Majesty

12:47.320 --> 12:49.270
and humbly plead for me?

12:49.270 --> 12:52.030
Well, just beg him.

12:52.360 --> 12:54.000
You and he are both
among the 3 Chief Ministers.

12:54.000 --> 12:56.510
He will give you some face.

12:56.510 --> 12:58.390
Forget it.

12:59.000 --> 13:00.910
Then I have no other way.

13:01.080 --> 13:02.030
You, this...

13:02.030 --> 13:02.510
I...

13:03.510 --> 13:06.320
I've already sent back the Desert Realm

13:06.320 --> 13:08.480
dancers you gave me.

13:08.480 --> 13:11.720
Please think of a way for me.

13:12.000 --> 13:13.000
Lord Wang.

13:13.320 --> 13:15.120
Am I that kind of person?

13:15.120 --> 13:17.200
I gave them to you fair and square.

13:17.200 --> 13:19.000
How can I just take them back now?

13:22.840 --> 13:24.150
I have no other choice.

13:25.120 --> 13:26.080
How about

13:27.120 --> 13:31.240
I take you alone to the palace...

13:32.270 --> 13:33.600
To meet His Majesty?

13:36.270 --> 13:37.870
That would be great.

13:40.390 --> 13:42.270
Let's go right now.

13:43.240 --> 13:43.630
Lord Wang.

13:43.630 --> 13:44.510
Wait, wait.

13:44.510 --> 13:45.510
Don't rush, don't rush.

13:45.510 --> 13:46.670
Lord Wang, look,

13:46.670 --> 13:49.440
how is my calligraphy?

13:49.750 --> 13:51.840
Riding on the crest of success.

13:51.840 --> 13:57.120
Yes, riding on the crest of success.

14:03.790 --> 14:06.320
Stories from ancient times
are fascinating.

14:06.790 --> 14:09.790
The 3 sworn brothers swore
an oath in the Peach Garden,

14:10.120 --> 14:11.670
set out to shape the fate of the realm,

14:11.670 --> 14:13.200
and achieved great things.

14:13.440 --> 14:14.510
Right, Lord Li?

14:17.600 --> 14:18.910
Coming to see me today,

14:19.270 --> 14:20.360
what is the matter?

14:20.670 --> 14:22.120
Your Majesty.

14:22.440 --> 14:24.510
Previously in the court,

14:24.510 --> 14:26.510
didn't Your Majesty,
in front of all officials,

14:26.510 --> 14:28.630
ask Lord Wang go home for a vacation?

14:29.240 --> 14:31.910
I don't think this is enough.

14:32.120 --> 14:33.360
He is guilty,

14:33.360 --> 14:34.690
and he must be punished.

14:34.720 --> 14:36.440
So today,

14:36.440 --> 14:40.240
I brought Wang Ruhai here
to see Your Majesty.

14:40.910 --> 14:42.840
It's so hot outside.

14:43.240 --> 14:45.100
Are you just going to let Lord Wang

14:45.670 --> 14:46.550
kneel outside like this?

14:46.550 --> 14:48.390
Your Majesty is absolutely right.

14:48.390 --> 14:50.720
But Wang Ruhai has
committed heinous crimes.

14:50.720 --> 14:53.840
Being punished in front of Your Majesty

14:53.840 --> 14:55.910
is his good fortune.

14:55.910 --> 14:56.440
All right.

14:56.440 --> 14:58.870
Tell Wang Ruhai to stop kneeling.

14:59.320 --> 15:00.600
He is getting old.

15:00.910 --> 15:02.770
Don't let him kneel himself sick.

15:03.360 --> 15:06.320
But about Wang Ruhai
staying at home idly...

15:08.390 --> 15:10.960
I punished him in front of

15:10.960 --> 15:12.440
so many civil and military officials.

15:12.440 --> 15:14.440
Can he be forgiven just by kneeling?

15:15.000 --> 15:16.860
Where would the law of the land be?

15:17.120 --> 15:18.720
And where would my authority be?

15:18.720 --> 15:19.910
Right, right.

15:20.000 --> 15:22.080
That's exactly what I told Wang Ruhai.

15:22.080 --> 15:25.080
But he's counting on
his merits in assisting the court.

15:25.080 --> 15:27.910
He also said he's willing
to accept punishment

15:27.910 --> 15:29.200
and kneel of his own accord.

15:29.200 --> 15:31.930
And if Your Majesty still
refuses to forgive him,

15:31.960 --> 15:32.870
he will...

15:33.000 --> 15:33.860
He will do what?

15:35.080 --> 15:37.240
It is inconvenient for me to say.

15:38.790 --> 15:41.080
If it's inconvenient, then don't say it.

15:41.910 --> 15:42.910
Tell him for me.

15:43.630 --> 15:45.120
I am a wise ruler.

15:45.630 --> 15:47.120
Before finding out the truth,

15:47.120 --> 15:49.200
I will not add more punishment to him.

15:49.320 --> 15:50.240
Let him go home

15:50.630 --> 15:52.160
and stay there peacefully.

15:52.270 --> 15:54.240
Thank you, Your Majesty.

15:54.240 --> 15:56.030
I will take my leave.

16:04.240 --> 16:05.390
What did His Majesty say?

16:05.390 --> 16:07.440
-Lord Wang.
-Tell me quickly.

16:07.510 --> 16:10.720
Alas, what could His Majesty say?

16:11.030 --> 16:12.000
His Majesty is

16:12.720 --> 16:15.480
still angry with you.

16:15.600 --> 16:18.390
If I hadn't pleaded for you in person,

16:18.550 --> 16:20.480
His Majesty would have
made you kneel here all day.

16:20.480 --> 16:21.510
Kneel all...

16:22.360 --> 16:23.200
This kid...

16:25.240 --> 16:27.670
I am, after all, a regent entrusted
by the late emperor.

16:27.670 --> 16:29.720
I have already kneeled to apologize,

16:29.720 --> 16:32.910
b-but he is still indifferent.

16:33.320 --> 16:33.670
No.

16:34.030 --> 16:36.080
I have to reason with him face to face.

16:36.080 --> 16:36.840
You can't do that.

16:36.840 --> 16:38.320
Don't stop me.

16:38.320 --> 16:39.200
Lord Wang.

16:39.600 --> 16:42.200
I have said all the good words.

16:42.200 --> 16:45.000
But His Majesty is in a bad mood.

16:45.240 --> 16:47.030
Let's go back and think it over.

16:47.030 --> 16:48.510
Let me tell you...

16:48.510 --> 16:49.390
My back, my legs,

16:49.390 --> 16:50.910
even my tailbone are all shot.

16:50.910 --> 16:52.790
Otherwise, I would have
gone to reason with him long ago.

16:52.790 --> 16:54.320
Slow down.

16:55.630 --> 16:56.870
At Tianlang Pass,

16:56.870 --> 16:58.480
I treated you well.

16:58.630 --> 16:59.870
Now that we are in your territory,

16:59.870 --> 17:01.440
you should treat me well.

17:02.360 --> 17:04.240
I'll make sure there's
plenty of good wine for you.

17:04.240 --> 17:04.770
Let's go.

17:23.720 --> 17:24.980
What's wrong with you?

17:29.240 --> 17:30.030
Nothing.

17:32.270 --> 17:34.400
No one saw you when you came, right?

17:34.510 --> 17:35.000
No.

17:35.680 --> 17:36.410
That's good.

17:37.240 --> 17:38.240
I've brought him.

17:53.310 --> 17:54.110
Mo.

17:55.720 --> 17:57.270
Mo, I'm sorry.

17:58.270 --> 17:59.920
I'm late.

17:59.920 --> 18:02.480
Mo, I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

18:07.510 --> 18:08.640
Don't be afraid, Mo.

18:09.590 --> 18:11.000
I will take you home.

18:27.510 --> 18:28.680
Mo is not dead.

18:31.070 --> 18:32.670
I saw it in Uncle Lie's notes.

18:32.680 --> 18:35.510
As long as we drive silver needles
through the major meridians

18:35.510 --> 18:37.040
and give him a Revival Pill,

18:38.000 --> 18:39.600
if he isn't completely gone,

18:40.200 --> 18:41.660
he won't die anytime soon—

18:42.030 --> 18:43.590
even if he doesn't wake up right away.

18:43.590 --> 18:44.590
The Revival Pill.

18:52.590 --> 18:53.510
Do you have water?

18:53.510 --> 18:54.160
Water?

18:54.270 --> 18:56.600
Where can we get water in this wilderness?

18:59.200 --> 19:00.000
What are you doing?

19:00.000 --> 19:00.920
Administer it with human blood.

19:00.920 --> 19:02.440
It might work even better.

19:02.880 --> 19:03.680
No.

19:04.270 --> 19:05.680
Do you have a better way?

19:06.680 --> 19:07.510
Let me do it.

19:15.680 --> 19:16.830
Enough.

19:16.830 --> 19:18.030
Enough.

19:36.880 --> 19:38.140
It seems to be working.

19:41.880 --> 19:42.590
Xiao Chi.

19:43.070 --> 19:43.830
Xiao Chi.

20:40.590 --> 20:41.480
You're awake.

20:41.960 --> 20:42.920
How do you feel?

20:43.070 --> 20:43.790
Much better.

20:43.790 --> 20:45.200
Here, drink some water.

20:56.480 --> 20:57.540
I feel much better.

20:59.400 --> 21:00.110
But,

21:00.640 --> 21:02.880
it would be great
if there was some wine right now.

21:02.880 --> 21:03.920
In your dreams.

21:04.400 --> 21:05.350
Even for this little bit of water,

21:05.350 --> 21:06.440
I had to walk a long way

21:06.440 --> 21:07.840
to find a family to get it.

21:08.310 --> 21:09.830
Give it to me when you're done.

21:09.830 --> 21:11.690
I still need it for Mo's medicine.

21:21.510 --> 21:22.310
Besides,

21:22.310 --> 21:24.070
with your current condition,

21:24.200 --> 21:26.530
you couldn't drink even if there was wine.

21:33.680 --> 21:34.830
From today on,

21:34.920 --> 21:36.880
I plan to treat you twice a day.

21:36.920 --> 21:38.780
That way, you'll recover faster.

21:38.880 --> 21:39.270
Okay.

21:40.030 --> 21:40.920
Once you're better,

21:40.920 --> 21:42.160
I can take Mo back to Changmo

21:42.160 --> 21:43.160
to find Uncle Lie.

21:53.070 --> 21:54.200
You can't leave.

21:58.070 --> 21:59.070
Why?

22:01.510 --> 22:02.160
His...

22:02.510 --> 22:04.680
His case file is blank.

22:05.110 --> 22:06.920
And he has been locked up
in the Imperial Prison for so many years,

22:06.920 --> 22:08.050
tortured every day.

22:08.240 --> 22:09.900
There must be a hidden secret.

22:10.000 --> 22:11.830
Then why can't I leave?

22:14.880 --> 22:16.010
The most urgent task

22:16.510 --> 22:18.040
is to settle him down first.

22:20.920 --> 22:22.050
Then what can you do?

22:28.310 --> 22:29.710
I'll take you somewhere.

22:30.270 --> 22:31.160
Seventeen?

22:32.240 --> 22:33.790
Haven't seen you in so many years.

22:33.790 --> 22:35.200
You really haven't changed a bit.

22:35.200 --> 22:36.920
Seventeen has been dead for years.

22:36.920 --> 22:38.720
That's her daughter, Eighteen.

22:40.240 --> 22:41.030
Master.

22:41.830 --> 22:42.640
How have you been?

22:42.640 --> 22:43.680
You little brat.

22:43.680 --> 22:44.740
Who is your master?

22:45.310 --> 22:46.110
Why are you here?

22:46.110 --> 22:48.030
If you have no business,
leave immediately.

22:48.030 --> 22:50.550
You're kicking me out
right after I arrived?

22:50.550 --> 22:53.210
You usually don't come to
me with anything good.

22:55.480 --> 22:57.070
Who is this?

23:00.030 --> 23:01.310
She is Han Yunling.

23:04.030 --> 23:04.880
You like her.

23:05.030 --> 23:06.310
What are you saying?

23:06.510 --> 23:08.170
I don't want to know who she is.

23:08.440 --> 23:09.720
What are you doing here?

23:09.720 --> 23:10.720
You have learned the martial arts,

23:10.720 --> 23:12.070
and I have passed
down the military books to you.

23:12.070 --> 23:13.310
Why are you still here?

23:13.310 --> 23:14.110
This time,

23:14.750 --> 23:16.950
I want you to help me look after someone.

23:21.510 --> 23:22.680
We haven't seen each other
for so many years,

23:22.680 --> 23:24.340
and you give me such a big gift.

23:24.510 --> 23:25.590
You brought a dead man here.

23:25.590 --> 23:26.310
What do you mean?

23:26.310 --> 23:27.590
He is not dead yet.

23:27.590 --> 23:29.310
What's the relationship between you two?

23:29.310 --> 23:30.400
He is my cousin.

23:30.680 --> 23:32.510
He has been locked up
in the Imperial Prison all these years.

23:32.510 --> 23:34.170
Xiao Chi helped me rescue him.

23:36.440 --> 23:39.400
Hey, he does still
have a little breath left.

23:40.200 --> 23:41.790
He is in this state right now.

23:41.790 --> 23:42.640
Who did this?

23:42.960 --> 23:43.510
It was me.

23:45.000 --> 23:45.830
How did you do it?

23:45.830 --> 23:46.640
I gave him...

23:51.830 --> 23:53.880
If you agree to let Mo stay here,

23:54.070 --> 23:56.070
I'll teach you how I did it.

23:56.200 --> 23:57.200
It's a deal.

24:00.070 --> 24:01.130
Within three days,

24:01.270 --> 24:02.790
you must find the best wine in the capital

24:02.790 --> 24:03.790
and bring it to me.

24:03.830 --> 24:05.110
If there is no good wine,

24:05.110 --> 24:05.920
I'll chop him up

24:05.920 --> 24:07.320
and feed him to Eighteen.

24:08.000 --> 24:10.400
Don't worry, I'll bring it
to you tomorrow.

24:10.920 --> 24:12.920
My father and I have
run a tavern for many years.

24:12.920 --> 24:14.520
Sir, don't try to deceive me.

24:14.720 --> 24:16.520
Miss, you don't know something.

24:17.000 --> 24:18.110
This shop

24:18.110 --> 24:20.160
is next to General Xiao's residence.

24:20.160 --> 24:23.000
It's also not far from
General Xiao's garrison.

24:23.000 --> 24:23.790
Say no more.

24:24.590 --> 24:25.880
I will

24:26.200 --> 24:27.790
rent this shop.

24:29.510 --> 24:30.720
You rented it just like that?

24:30.720 --> 24:32.200
Isn't it too hasty?

24:32.720 --> 24:33.880
How could it be?

24:35.030 --> 24:35.960
Here is the rent.

24:36.790 --> 24:38.790
Miss, you are a straightforward person.

24:38.790 --> 24:40.880
Then I wish your tavern

24:41.110 --> 24:42.270
a prosperous business.

24:42.270 --> 24:43.870
Thank you for your blessing.

24:46.550 --> 24:49.440
Lust is a blade

24:49.880 --> 24:51.480
that cuts deep.

24:56.480 --> 24:57.160
Lord Fei.

24:57.160 --> 24:58.720
You are here so early.

24:59.030 --> 25:00.240
I agreed with your general yesterday

25:00.240 --> 25:01.110
to move here today.

25:01.110 --> 25:01.920
Where is he?

25:02.590 --> 25:04.030
He went out yesterday during the day

25:04.030 --> 25:05.690
and didn't come back at night.

25:06.310 --> 25:07.200
He just returned to the capital,

25:07.200 --> 25:09.110
and he hasn't finished
his work at the residence.

25:09.110 --> 25:10.310
What is so important?

25:10.510 --> 25:11.840
I don't know about that.

25:13.590 --> 25:14.240
All right.

25:14.240 --> 25:16.510
I don't know how much
longer I have to wait for him.

25:16.510 --> 25:17.370
Go do your work.

25:17.550 --> 25:18.070
Yes.

25:20.880 --> 25:21.680
Zheng?

25:25.920 --> 25:27.320
So you're only just back?

25:27.880 --> 25:29.410
Where did you go last night?

25:30.680 --> 25:31.810
I had some business.

25:32.070 --> 25:33.030
Never mind.

25:33.200 --> 25:34.270
The child has grown up

25:34.270 --> 25:35.670
and can't be controlled.

25:36.590 --> 25:38.400
Come with me to the West Courtyard.

25:38.400 --> 25:39.160
West Courtyard?

25:39.160 --> 25:40.490
Don't just stand there.

25:47.240 --> 25:48.700
Why are you standing here?

25:48.720 --> 25:49.720
My lords.

25:49.790 --> 25:51.510
Her Highness is still sleeping.

25:51.510 --> 25:53.400
Still sleeping at this hour?

25:53.480 --> 25:54.920
Her Highness is of noble birth,

25:54.920 --> 25:56.590
and the journey has been exhausting.

25:56.590 --> 25:58.990
She needs more sleep
to recover her energy.

25:59.510 --> 26:01.000
Could she not be inside?

26:04.550 --> 26:06.030
Her Highness is still resting.

26:06.030 --> 26:07.440
If you dare to overstep your bounds,

26:07.440 --> 26:09.240
don't blame me for how I respond.

26:09.310 --> 26:11.640
Jin Xi, let them in.
